description: Yo, Austin!If any of yinz are craving a pitch perfect Pittsburgh meal right in the pit of your stomach, you’re in luck because these Steelers fans are wheelin’ their truck through the streets and serving up all your favorite East Coast eats. You’ll find that you can dine on all your favorite Pittsburgh dishes:Their Point Park Pierogies topped with butter and onions are just plain delicious. The Pitts Burger, Penn Hill Pretzels, and Frick Park Fried Rice, are only a few of the items that will take you right back to everything nice about The ‘Burgh. So all yinz Pennsylvanians-at-heart be sure to convene and pencil in a visit to “Yinz Hungry?” for this powerfully pleasing cuisine.
name: Yinz Hungry?
